what: The runaway thread of Citizen of the Galaxy — sold as a slave, raised by a spy, adopted by Free Traders, conscripted by the Guard, and at last revealed as Thor Bradley Rudbek, lost heir to the greatest shipbuilding fortune in the Terran sphere.
